My wish for you in 2021 is to rediscover the power of vulnerability.Start with asking or answering the question, “How are you?” How do you become whole again after trauma breaks you open? This poignant question formed part of an interview with Michaela Coel, the writer of I May Destroy You, an unnerving show which dramatises her sexual assault. The story was featured in Vulture.com.
I think the answer to becoming whole again lies in sincerely answering the question, “How are you?



